tafsir[9]{c,v,t}:
  30,33,"Si sa…óteende memii sirkoo…ìe …ìen, immorde e √±awu maa baasal maa kokke, …ìe nodda Joomi ma…ì…ìe tun, ruttitorgol e Makko yankinagol moolo e makko, fii no O huncirana …ìe sa…óteende ma…ì…ìe. Hooti si O yurmiraama …ìe huncangol …ìe nden sa…óteende, e jaka fedde e ma…ì…ìe hino yiltitoo e sirkangol kafida Joomi mun e go…ó…óum goo ka du'agol."
  30,34,"Si …ìe yeddi neemaaji Alla …óin, wano yeddugol …ìe neema huncaneede sa…óteende nden, wonii …ìe dakmitorii ko …ìe jogitii e …óam nguurndam, arma …ìe yi'iroya gite ma…ì…ìe …óen √ëalnde Darngal, wonnde ko e majjere …ìanngunde …ìe wonunoo e mun."
  30,35,"Ko naadi …ìe e sirkangol Alla ko aldaa e hujja? Menen, Men jippinaali e ma…ì…ìe hujja Deftere, mo …ìe dallinorta e ko …ìe sirkanta Alla kon. ∆Åe alaa kadi deftere yewtaynde fii sirku ma…ì…ìe on, qirritantoonde …ìe sellugol ko …ìe yeddaynoo kon."
  30,36,"Si Men mee…óinirii yim…ìe …ìen gootel e neemaaji Amen …óin, wano cellal e ngalu, …ìe weltora …óum weltaare dullere e townitaare. Si tawnii non ko bone on memirii …ìe - wano √±awu e baasal - sabu ko juu…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen faggitori kon geddi, …óum haray …ìe ta∆¥ike yurmeende Alla nden, …ìe sikka …óum …óon iwataa e ma…ì…ìe."
  30,37,"E …ìee yi'aali, wonnde Alla no ya√±√±ana arsike on mo O muuyani e jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen, fii ndaarnda- gol …ìe si …ìe yettay Mo maa si …ìe yedday? Himo …ìi…ótinana Mo kadi on Mo O muuyani e ma…ì…ìe, fii anndugol si o mu√±√±oto maa o mu√±√±oo? Wonii e …óum, maandeeji wonannde gom…óim…ìe neweende e yurmeende Alla nden."
  30,38,"An juul…óo on, jonnu jom-…ìadal ngal ko o haandi ko, ka mo∆¥∆¥ugol e ka jokkugol en…óam, okkaa hatonjin…óo kadi ko humtanta mo haaju mum, walla-…óaa tumarankeejo wo…ó…óitii…óo leydi mun. Ko ngool okkugol e …óeen geece …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude wonande …ìen faalaa…ìe yarluyee Alla on; ko …ìen huntoo…ìe …óin haajuuji kadi, woni maliroytee…ìe he…ìugol Aljanna mo …ìe …óa…ì…ìaynoo, …ìe hisa e lepte …óe …ìe hulunoo."
  30,39,"Kala ko jonnir…óon yim…ìe …ìen e jawle, fii no …óe artira e mon …ìeydaari(riba), annde …óe …ìeydotaako ka Alla. Kala non ko jonnir…óon e jawle mon …óen, fii ko duncitoree haaju, hara hi…óon …óa…ì…ìira …óum yarluyee Alla, wanaa darja maa manteede, ko …ìen …óon woni sowanoytee…ìe njo…ìdi ka Alla."
  30,40,"Ko Alla gooto On hertori tagugol on, refti arsikugol on, refti warugol on wuurnita. Hara no e sanamuuji mon, …ói rewoton gaanin Makko …óin, wa…óayndu go…ó…óum e …óin? Senayee woodanii Mo! O toowii e ko sirkoo…ìe …ìen wowlata …ìe fi…ìa."
  30,41,"Bone on fee√±irii ka njorndi e ka maaje, …óuytagol nguurndam yim…ìe …ìen e wonkiiji ma…ì…ìe, nawnaaje e √±abbuuli; sabu ko …ìe golli e geddi. ∆äum fee√±irii fii no Alla mee…óinira …ìe njo…ìdi yoga e ko …ìe bonnuno e nguurndam aduna …óam; belajo'o, …ìe ruttoray e Makko tuubugol."